{"words":[{"word":"talos","count":3},{"word":"black","count":2},{"word":"alley","count":2},{"word":"place","count":2},{"word":"came","count":2},{"word":"wanted","count":2},{"word":"choice","count":2},{"word":"terminal","count":2},{"word":"thank","count":2},{"word":"waterway","count":2},{"word":"name","count":1},{"word":"colleen","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"friends","count":1},{"word":"gang","count":1},{"word":"destroyed","count":1},{"word":"another","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"vagrants","count":1},{"word":"scraps","count":1},{"word":"couple","count":1},{"word":"jobs","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"smoke","count":1},{"word":"claiming","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"owned","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"follow","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"steal","count":1},{"word":"lie","count":1},{"word":"cheat","count":1},{"word":"rob","count":1},{"word":"old","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"tribute","count":1},{"word":"beating","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"ones","count":1},{"word":"dirty","count":1},{"word":"hands","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"easy","count":1},{"word":"main","count":1},{"word":"reason","count":1},{"word":"stand","count":1},{"word":"lets","count":1},{"word":"transform","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"powerful","count":1},{"word":"echo","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"hurt","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"underground","count":1},{"word":"abandoned","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"clean","count":1},{"word":"livable","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"pipes","count":1},{"word":"maze","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"split","count":1},{"word":"territory","count":1},{"word":"rank","count":1},{"word":"holed","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"deep","count":1},{"word":"h-hey","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"pretend","count":1},{"word":"hideout","count":1},{"word":"slippery","count":1},{"word":"wrong","count":1},{"word":"move","count":1},{"word":"gone","count":1},{"word":"gondola","count":1},{"word":"blink","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"My name is Colleen... Please, help me and my friends.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"I'm from the Black Alley...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"No, no, no... The Black Alley is more than just the gang! It's the place too.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"You're right, Talos destroyed it. But there's another way in...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"It used to be a home for vagrants like us. A few scraps, a couple of jobs... just enough to get by.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"But then she came, and it all went up in smoke...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"She came in claiming this place was hers since they owned it before.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Told us, if we wanted to stay, we had to follow her rules. No other choice.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Steal, lie, cheat, rob... same as the old days. Give her your tribute, or... or you get a beating.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Some people did. They wanted to, you know? The ones with the dirty hands already. They were easy.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"But the main reason is that no one can stand up to her...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"I... I...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"A Terminal... Talos also has a Terminal. It lets her transform into a powerful Echo.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"I'm sorry...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Thank you, thank you both!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"I didn't...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"I… I didn't have a choice! If I didn't, they'd... they'd...you know, hurt me!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"But… but I…","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Fine... I get it.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Don't worry. It may be an underground waterway, but it's been abandoned for a long time now.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"It's not exactly clean, but it's livable. We did some work on it.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"The pipes are a maze, though. They split up the territory by rank...","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"Talos is holed up somewhere deep in the waterway.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"H-hey… I'll pretend I don't know who you are!","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"That's his hideout. Over there.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014},{"text":"He's a slippery one. One wrong move, and he'll be gone, off in a Gondola before you can blink.","quest_name":"A Blaze in the Dark","quest_id":158800014}]}